    "EVIDENCE STANDARD: Compliance-critical items require verbatim quotes with page+section. Missing items must be labeled: NOT FOUND after review of pages X\u2013Y (or NOT PROVIDED if document absent).",
    "COVERAGE GATING: Use only authoritative allowlists (states_by_name and counties_by_fips). Pins/authority lists are visual-only; not gating evidence.",
    "FEDERAL ELIGIBILITY: If Active SAM is required and proof is not provided => NO-BID.",
    "PRICING: Delivered direct cost basis only. Financing costs must be embedded (financing uplift) if used.",
    "CONFIDENTIALITY: Do not disclose internal credit limits, cash constraints, or financing terms in public bids unless explicitly required."
  ],
